theorem closure_interior_union_eq
    {X : Type*} [TopologicalSpace X] {A B : Set X} :
    closure (interior (A ∪ B : Set X)) =
      closure (interior A) ∪ closure (interior B) := by
  have hInt : interior (A ∪ B : Set X) = interior A ∪ interior B := by
    simpa using interior_union
  calc
    closure (interior (A ∪ B : Set X))
        = closure (interior A ∪ interior B) := by
          simpa [hInt]
    _ = closure (interior A) ∪ closure (interior B) := by
          simpa using closure_union

theorem interior_closure_union
    {X : Type*} [TopologicalSpace X] {A B : Set X} :
    interior (closure (A ∪ B : Set X)) =
      interior (closure (A : Set X) ∪ closure (B : Set X)) := by
  simpa [closure_union]
